Comment: Hi everyone!  Just when you thought you had forgotten all about me and thought you had all escaped Old Matey's clutches ...... Well, here I'm back!  I have just completed Elyhim/Terrence's Modern Benoni MT and at least I managed to complete it with a win and come 6th.  For a long time I did not look like winning, but at the last moment there was a twist to the tale.  So, how did this all happen?  Well, read on ........
